Basic building blocks
1) Module-To import 3rd party Modules(root module -app.module.ts)
2)Component - To create html,css and ts files
Basic components

1) To  create new project - ng new project-name
2)To create new Component-ng g c Component-name
3)To run angular files -ng serve --open

basic concepts

Data binding
Share data between components
ts-->components
html-->view

1-One way data binding
data sharing only one direction(ts-->html or html-->ts)

a)String interpolation -{{expression}}
b)property binding-[palceholder]="name"

1.2)View to component
a)event binding -(event-name)="function()"(from html-->ts)
b) event binding using $event-(event-name)="function-name($event)"
c)event binding using template referencing variable-#variable_name


2)
2 way data finding
data sharing only two direction(ts-->html and html-->ts)

